{"tid":1017524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九陰真經 台服成班香港人","createTime":"2019-02-11T13:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T10:55:59.000Z","uid":187569,"like":3,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"de80127a1c4e95129e5fc92d23dd175b138384c2","tid":1017524,"uid":187569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"九陰真經 台服 天星伴月 暫時啱啱開咗一個月多啲 <br />\n我哋二三十個香港人,<br />\n暫時全個伺服器分咗三大勢力 一邊係我哋香港人  一邊係一班台灣大陸仔(數據顯示我哋贏佢一千個頭) 仲有部分人喺中立 <br />\n如果有興趣加入嘅巴打,有幾個途徑幫你哋即刻跟上進度.<br />\ni.幫你搵師傅(好多優惠)即刻升上嚟,馬上跟到進度<br />\nii.畀個空殼帳號你,即係有開住升開嘢但係冇嘢喺入面.可以慳番啲進度<br />\niii.分資源畀新手<br />\n<br />\n有興趣玩嘅巴打可以<br />\n直接入RC:27832190<br />\nTG@whatchakyousaying"},{"pid":"f0aa7cc5d67f1023e9055c7de46a83d5a78a7034","tid":1017524,"uid":187569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6175b4db387f13343c1b8dd83d0e842495fe1524","tid":1017524,"uid":71433,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"三大勢力 睇到已經笑到噴飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0004413e25560beafdbb866bb3d3313a8afa7c2","tid":1017524,"uid":187569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6175b4db387f13343c1b8dd83d0e842495fe1524","tid":1017524,"uid":71433,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:48:51.000Z","msg":"三大勢力 睇到已經笑到噴飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"除咗呢三大都無其他啦，嚴格來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6aee799b8f4e8f9d5c79a694eb519fcbb85306","tid":1017524,"uid":187569,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T14:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"